# Raw profiler artifacts are large and fully regenerable from the drivers
# (bench/profile/*) -- keep them local, don't bloat the repo. The small
# JSON baselines under results/ (micro.json, mn.json, pytest_benchmark/)
# ARE committed: they are the regression-gate inputs.
results/profiles/*.svg
results/profiles/*.folded
results/profiles/*.data
*.perf
perf.data*
